{{>layout/header}}

<div id="container">
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="my-page">
            <div class="title-area">
                <div class="top-area">
                    <a class="location" href="/"><img class="icon" src="/images/app/home.png" alt="HOME"></a>
                    <span class="location">활동 내역</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="content-area">
                <div class="activity-history-area">
                    {{#history}}
                    <h2><a href="/users/activity-history/posts/{{userId}}">{{nickname}}</a> 님의 활동 내역</h2>
                    <div class="top-area">
                        <p>가입일: {{createdDate}}</p>
                        <p>작성 글: {{numOfPosts}}</p>
                        <p>작성 댓글: {{numOfComments}}</p>
                        {{#admin}}<p>누적 신고 횟수: 게시글 - {{numOfPostReports}}, 댓글 - {{numOfCommentReports}}, 사용자 - {{numOfUserReports}}</p>
                        <p class="user-ban">누적 정지 횟수: {{^bannedUsersExistence}}0{{/bannedUsersExistence}}{{#bannedUsersExistence}}{{count}} ({{period}}, {{startedDate}} ~ {{expiredDate}}){{/bannedUsersExistence}}</p>
                        <div class="btn-area">
                            <button type="button" class="btn" id="btn-user-ban">활동 정지</button>
                        </div>{{/admin}}
                    </div>
                    <div class="posts-area">
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                <a style="background-color: #C1DAC0;" href="/users/activity-history/posts/{{userId}}">게시글</a></li><li>
                            <a href="/users/activity-history/comments/{{userId}}">댓글</a></li>
                        </ul>
                        <table>
                            <thead>
                                <tr>
                                    <th class="no">번호</th>
                                    <th class="post">게시글</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                            {{^posts.content}}
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="no-content" colspan="2">작성한 글이 없어요.</td>
                                </tr>
                            {{/posts.content}}
                            {{#posts.content}}
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="no-checkbox">{{id}}</td>
                                    <td>
                                        <div class="tit">
                                            <a href="/posts/read/{{id}}">{{title}}</a>
                                        </div>
                                        <span class="date">{{author}} | {{modifiedDate}} | <img class="view"> {{view}} | <img class="cmt"> {{comments}} | <img class="like"> {{likes}}</span>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            {{/posts.content}}
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                        {{#pages}}
                            <div>
                                {{#hasPrevious}}
                                    첫 페이지: <a href="/users/activity-history/posts/{{userId}}?page={{firstPage}}">{{firstPage}}</a> | 이전 페이지: <a href="/users/activity-history/posts/{{userId}}?page={{previousPage}}">{{previousPage}}</a> |
                                {{/hasPrevious}}
                                {{#displayPages}}
                                    {{#isCurrentPage}}
                                        | 현재 페이지: {{page}}
                                    {{/isCurrentPage}}
                                    {{^isCurrentPage}}
                                        | <a href="/users/activity-history/posts/{{userId}}?page={{page}}">{{page}}</a>
                                    {{/isCurrentPage}}
                                {{/displayPages}}
                                {{#hasNext}}
                                    | | 다음 페이지: <a href="/users/activity-history/posts/{{userId}}?page={{nextPage}}">{{nextPage}}</a> | 마지막 페이지: <a href="/users/activity-history/posts/{{userId}}?page={{lastPage}}">{{lastPage}}</a>
                                {{/hasNext}}
                            </div>
                        {{/pages}}
                    </div>
                    {{/history}}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

{{>layout/footer}}
<script src="/js/app/my-page.js"></script>
</body>
</html>